<h2 id="0-dot-11-dot-0"><span class="timestamp-wrapper"><span class="timestamp">&lt;2025-05-19 Mon&gt; </span></span> <strong>0.11.0</strong></h2>
<p>Added user system prompts management</p>
<ul>
<li>You can now save, load and manage system prompts</li>
<li>Created new transient menu for user system prompts (C-c s)</li>
<li>Organized prompts by categories with org-mode format storage</li>
